* Lagrange Multiplier Tests
use xxx, clear
quietly regress variable1 variable2 
predict ehat, residual
gen ehat2=ehat^2
quietly regress ehat2 variable2 
di "NR2 = " e(N)*e(r2)
di "5% critical value = " invchi2tail(e(df_m),.05)
di "P-value = " chi2tail(e(df_m),e(N)*e(r2))

